## ONNX model weights — track via Git LFS
##
## NOTE: This config is set up so future changes to the model files use LFS,
## but the existing files committed in `Phase 5 Try 1` (d14fc8d) still live
## in plain git history. To migrate the existing files into LFS (rewrites
## that commit), run:
##
##   git lfs install
##   git lfs migrate import --include="public/models/*.onnx" --everything
##   git push --force-with-lease origin main
##
## Only do this if you've checked you are the sole pusher to main.
public/models/*.onnx filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
